title: Kendall and Kylie Jenner don bikinis as they cuddle to promote their clothing collection
text:
Kylie Jenner may be the world's youngest self-made billionaire, but sister Kendall is the world's highest-paid model.

And she recently teamed up with her little sis to model some designs from their latest Kendall + Kylie collection.

The sisters showed some skin in a bizarrely sultry photo they posted Tuesday to the brand's Instagram.

Sister act: Kendall and Kylie Jenner showed some skin in a bizarrely sultry photo they posted Tuesday to Instagram

Kendall sported a leopard-print string bikini with a sheer black and white tie-dye long-sleeve shirt.

The 23-year-old completed the sexy ensemble with a brown stetson for a music festival chic aesthetic.

Kylie, 22, wore an equally revealing bikini, which she paired with a fuzzy neon yellow sweater.

Kendall lounged around on top of Kylie in a bizarre position that led many followers to assume they posted another Photoshop fail.

Teamwork: They teamed up to model some designs from their latest Kendall + Kylie collection

Behind-the-scenes: The promo photo comes days after they shared a video of themselves modeling in front of the same backdrop for the collection

One user wrote in the photo's comments: 'Yea.... The editing is just very off in this pic.'

The promo photo comes days after they shared a video of themselves modeling in front of the same backdrop for the collection.

Kendall also took to her own Instagram story with a glimpse behind-the-scenes of the shoot.

It shows her sitting in the grass by a pool as she sports a white two-piece bikini and an impossibly wide-brimmed straw hat with red, orange and green stripes.

Afterward, she lived dangerously as she filmed herself driving around, wearing a filter that gave her freckles and butterflies on her face.

Bikini babe: Kendall also took to her own Instagram story with a glimpse behind-the-scenes of the shoot, in which she sports a white bikini
